# Monolyth repo rules
- Do not create duplicate routes.
- API routes live under app/api/**.
- Public viewer is app/share/[id] (singular).
- Shares API is app/api/shares/* (plural).
- Events API is app/api/events/* (singular).
- DB columns: versions.doc_id; events.event_type (NOT NULL).
- Next.js 16: await params (params is a Promise).
- Prefer full-file replacements; keep styling minimal and consistent.
